{"tid":882300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"籲勿留空間給反對派   馮煒光：將來是分裂中國的隱患","createTime":"2018-10-30T04:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T06:14:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b02b588534fb9de518330a632e30e09d33b026de","tid":882300,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"前新聞統籌專員馮煒光昨日在《HKGpao》以「 『ABC』原來是用來騙中央的﹗」為題撰文評論政事，他在文中指「反對派的民主是以『推翻中共執政、促成中國支爆』為前提的」呼籲勿留空間給派，他提到「反對派繼續獲得議席，將來是分裂中國的隱患，因為西方要分裂中國，最方便一定從香港入手，而不是北京、上海和廣州等內地大城市。為免逾10 億計中國人民生靈塗炭，特區政府理應負起政治責任，不留任何空間給反對派。因為他們是分裂中國的歷史罪人﹗」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F/39206/-%E5%BC%95%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%88%92-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E7%95%99%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E7%B5%A6%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE--%E9%A6%AE%E7%85%92%E5%85%89-%E5%B0%87%E4%BE%86%E6%98%AF%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%B1%E6%82%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%2594%259F%2F39206%2F-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2588%2592-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%258B%25BF%25E7%2595%2599%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE--%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%2585%2592%25E5%2585%2589-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259A%25B1%25E6%2582%25A3&d=%2BpoJmaSyVHiK8oM95kKNaUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=31ad1629\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F/39206/-%E5%BC%95%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%88%92-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E7%95%99%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E7%B5%A6%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE--%E9%A6%AE%E7%85%92%E5%85%89-%E5%B0%87%E4%BE%86%E6%98%AF%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%B1%E6%82%A3</a>"},{"pid":"edc0fdfcffacf83910e2d2a8761e2056c3fd18cc","tid":882300,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-